name: Custom Order Maid 3D2&2.5+: X1+Vol.01
summary: This DLC adds X1 compatibility for 5 personalities. You'll get to play special honeymoon events and yotogi as well as a Fishing minigame. Maids will now be compatible with the following events: 1. New Mode “Honeymoon Mode” 2. ”Honeymoon Yotogi” 3. ”NTR Honeymoon”
